{"thag1.70:0.1":"Theragatha 1.70 ","thag1.70:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","thag1.70:0.3":"Sattamavagga ","thag1.70:0.4":"Punnattheragatha ","thag1.70:1.1":"“Silameva idha aggam, ","thag1.70:1.2":"pannava pana uttamo; ","thag1.70:1.3":"Manussesu ca devesu, ","thag1.70:1.4":"silapannanato jayan”ti. ","thag1.70:1.5":"… Punno thero … ","thag1.70:1.6":"vaggo sattamo. ","thag1.70:2.0":"Tassuddanam ","thag1.70:2.1":"Vappo ca vajjiputto ca, ","thag1.70:2.2":"pakkho vimalakondanno; ","thag1.70:2.3":"Ukkhepakatavaccho ca, ","thag1.70:2.4":"meghiyo ekadhammiko; ","thag1.70:2.5":"Ekudaniyachanna ca, ","thag1.70:2.6":"punnatthero mahabbaloti. "}